The paper proposes a new neural network model that sequentially selects local transformations at each layer, which increases the expression power of the model. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on the model architecture and learning algorithm rather than specific applications, the first three sub-categories are more likely than the latter two.
